<p><span style="font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">我校<span style="font-family: Calibri">2022</span>年</span><span style="font-family: 宋体">退役</span><span style="font-family: 宋体">大学</span><span style="font-family: 宋体">士兵免试专升本</span><span style="font-family: 宋体">第一批次录取工作已经结束，目前尚有部分缺额计划，现将志愿征集公告如下：</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">一、征集对象</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: Calibri"><span style="font-family: 宋体">所有已报名</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体">但</span><span style="font-family: Calibri"><span style="font-family: 宋体">未</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体">被</span><span style="font-family: Calibri"><span style="font-family: 宋体">录取的退役大学生士兵，均可</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体">参加我校志愿征集（含未参加我校面试考查的考生）。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">二、志愿填报</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">符合征集志愿条件的</span><span style="font-family: Calibri"><span style="font-family: 宋体">退役大学生士兵</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体">，请于<span style="font-family: Calibri">3</span>月<span style="font-family: Calibri">18</span>日<span style="font-family: Calibri">9</span>：<span style="font-family: Calibri">00-17</span>：<span style="font-family: Calibri">00</span>通过省考试院官网填报征集志愿，每个考生只能填报<span style="font-family: Calibri">1</span>个缺额征集志愿。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family: 宋体">三、征集专业和计划</span></span></p><table cellspacing="0" width="512"><tbody><tr style="height: 41px" class="firstRow"><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" valign="center" width="61"><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">院校</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px"><br/></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">代号</span></p></td><td style="padding: 0px 7px; border-left: none; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: